.DT
crouch
Discworld player help
crouch

.SH Name
.SI 5
crouch - Change your position to crouching.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
crouch
crouch on the floor
crouch on <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to change your position.  To crouch on the floor, or to crouch on
something, or to just crouch down if you are sitting.
.EP


.SH Examples
.SI 5
> crouch
You crouch down.
> crouch on the floor
You crouch on the floor.
> crouch on table
You crouch on the table.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
kneel, stand, lie, meditate, sit
.EP
